apiVersion: apiextensions.k8s.io/v1beta1
kind: CustomResourceDefinition
metadata:

  labels:
    helm.sh/chart: kfserving-1.1.0
    app.kubernetes.io/name: kfserving

spec:
  additionalPrinterColumns:
  - JSONPath: .status.url
    name: URL
    type: string
  - JSONPath: .status.conditions[?(@.type=='Ready')].status
    name: Ready
    type: string

    name: Age

  group: serving.kubeflow.org
  names:
    kind: TrainedModel
    listKind: TrainedModelList

      properties:

                  x-kubernetes-int-or-string: true

              required:

              type: object
          required:

        status:
          properties:
            address:

              type: object

              items:

            url:
              type: string
          type: object
      type: object

    storage: true

data.test_all.py:
import os

import requests


def test_controller_service_connection():
    url = "https://release-name-kfserving-controller.default.svc:9443/"
    verify = "/controller-tls-secret/ca.crt"

    response = requests.get(url, verify=verify)

    assert response.status_code == 404


def test_controller_metrics_service_connection():
    url = "http://release-name-kfserving-controller-metrics:8080/metrics"

    response = requests.get(url)

    assert response.status_code == 200


def test_models_web_app_service_connection():
    url = "http://release-name-kfserving-models-web-app:5000/"

    response = requests.get(url)

    assert response.status_code == 200
